text: hum tamari ane temani vacce majabuta dhala banavi da'um chum, mane lokhandani cadaro lavi apo, tyam sudhi ke jyare te banne parvato vacce divala barabara banavi didhi to adesa apyo ke aga bhadakavo, jyare te lokhandani cadarone taddana agamam pheravi didhi, to kahyum ke mari pase lavo, tena para pigalelum tambu nankhi do
